{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 6,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "iJpuSZDxZSBJHFSeavba",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "sister-m"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 482.335,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.019,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "The words of Jacob, the brother of Nephi,",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.199,
      "end": 5.939,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he spake unto the people of Nephi:",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 6.619,
      "end": 9.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.307,
      "end": 12.186,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Jacob, having been called of God,",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 12.366,
      "end": 16.546,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ordained after the manner of his holy order,",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 16.726,
      "end": 20.581,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and having been consecrated by my brother Nephi,",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 20.761,
      "end": 24.151,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto whom ye look as a king or a protector,",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 24.331,
      "end": 26.653,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and on whom ye depend for safety,",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 26.833,
      "end": 32.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold ye know that I have spoken unto you exceedingly many things.",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 32.714,
      "end": 35.082,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, I speak unto you again;",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 35.262,
      "end": 39.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I am desirous for the welfare of your souls.",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 39.436,
      "end": 42.501,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, mine anxiety is great for you;",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 42.681,
      "end": 46.303,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye yourselves know that it ever has been.",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 46.483,
      "end": 49.641,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I have exhorted you with all diligence;",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 49.821,
      "end": 53.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I have taught you the words of my father;",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 53.345,
      "end": 58.128,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I have spoken unto you concerning all things which are written,",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 58.308,
      "end": 60.491,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the creation of the world.",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 61.171,
      "end": 64.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, behold, I would speak unto you",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 64.88,
      "end": 66.83,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning things which are,",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 67.01,
      "end": 68.403,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and which are to come;",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 68.583,
      "end": 71.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I will read you the words of Isaiah.",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 72.06,
      "end": 77.633,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they are the words which my brother has desired that I should speak unto you.",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 77.813,
      "end": 80.507,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I speak unto you for your sakes,",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 80.687,
      "end": 84.774,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye may learn and glorify the name of your God.",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 85.454,
      "end": 90.934,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, the words which I shall read are they which Isaiah spake",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 91.114,
      "end": 93.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning all the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 93.616,
      "end": 96.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they may be likened unto you,",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 96.629,
      "end": 98.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for ye are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 99.177,
      "end": 103.403,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there are many things which have been spoken by Isaiah",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 103.583,
      "end": 106.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which may be likened unto you,",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 106.364,
      "end": 108.872,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because ye are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 109.552,
      "end": 111.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, these are the words:",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 111.915,
      "end": 113.587,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thus saith the Lord God:",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 113.767,
      "end": 117.714,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I will lift up mine hand to the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 117.894,
      "end": 120.448,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and set up my standard to the people;",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 120.628,
      "end": 123.647,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall bring thy sons in their arms,",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 123.827,
      "end": 127.821,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thy daughters shall be carried upon their shoulders.",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 128.001,
      "end": 147.738,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, these are the words: Thus saith the Lord God: Behold, I will lift up mine hand to the Gentiles, and set up my standard to the people; and they shall bring thy sons in their arms, and thy daughters shall be carried upon their shoulders.",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 148.418,
      "end": 151.576,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And kings shall be thy nursing fathers,",
      "verse": "6:7",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 151.756,
      "end": 154.403,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their queens thy nursing mothers;",
      "verse": "6:7",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 154.583,
      "end": 158.995,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall bow down to thee with their faces towards the earth,",
      "verse": "6:7",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 159.175,
      "end": 161.636,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and lick up the dust of thy feet;",
      "verse": "6:7",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 161.816,
      "end": 164.37,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thou shalt know that I am the Lord;",
      "verse": "6:7",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 164.55,
      "end": 167.429,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they shall not be ashamed that wait for me.",
      "verse": "6:7",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 167.609,
      "end": 188.693,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And kings shall be thy nursing fathers, and their queens thy nursing mothers; they shall bow down to thee with their face toward faces towards the earth, and lick up the dust of thy feet; and thou shalt know that I am the Lord; for they shall not be ashamed that wait for me.",
      "verse": "6:7",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 189.373,
      "end": 193.738,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Jacob, would speak somewhat concerning these words.",
      "verse": "6:8",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 193.918,
      "end": 196.565,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, the Lord has shown me",
      "verse": "6:8",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 196.745,
      "end": 199.16,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that those who were at Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "6:8",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 199.34,
      "end": 200.826,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from whence we came,",
      "verse": "6:8",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 201.006,
      "end": 203.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "have been slain and carried away captive.",
      "verse": "6:8",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 204.565,
      "end": 207.584,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, the Lord has shown unto me",
      "verse": "6:9",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 207.764,
      "end": 209.714,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they should return again.",
      "verse": "6:9",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 209.894,
      "end": 212.262,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also has shown unto me",
      "verse": "6:9",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 212.442,
      "end": 227.628,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God, the Holy One of Israel,",
      "verse": "6:9",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 227.808,
      "end": 231.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should manifest himself unto them in the flesh;",
      "verse": "6:9",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 231.61,
      "end": 234.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after he should manifest himself",
      "verse": "6:9",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 234.576,
      "end": 237.27,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should scourge him and crucify him,",
      "verse": "6:9",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 237.45,
      "end": 241.351,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words of the angel who spake it unto me.",
      "verse": "6:9",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 242.031,
      "end": 244.957,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they have hardened their hearts",
      "verse": "6:10",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 245.137,
      "end": 246.948,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and stiffened their necks",
      "verse": "6:10",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 247.128,
      "end": 249.311,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "against the Holy One of Israel,",
      "verse": "6:10",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 249.491,
      "end": 254.924,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the judgments of the Holy One of Israel shall come upon them.",
      "verse": "6:10",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 255.104,
      "end": 259.562,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the day cometh that they shall be smitten and afflicted.",
      "verse": "6:10",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 260.242,
      "end": 263.493,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, after they are driven to and fro,",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 263.673,
      "end": 265.623,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus saith the angel,",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 265.803,
      "end": 268.357,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many shall be afflicted in the flesh,",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 268.537,
      "end": 271.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall not be suffered to perish,",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 271.364,
      "end": 273.732,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the prayers of the faithful;",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 273.912,
      "end": 277.674,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be scattered, and smitten, and hated;",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 277.854,
      "end": 281.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, the Lord will be merciful unto them,",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 281.61,
      "end": 285.093,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that when they shall come to the knowledge of their Redeemer,",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 285.273,
      "end": 289.731,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be gathered together again to the lands of their inheritance.",
      "verse": "6:11",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 290.411,
      "end": 292.733,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And blessed are the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 292.913,
      "end": 295.514,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they of whom the prophet has written;",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 295.694,
      "end": 299.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, if it so be that they shall repent",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 299.403,
      "end": 301.539,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and fight not against Zion,",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 301.719,
      "end": 306.456,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and do not unite themselves to that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 306.636,
      "end": 308.447,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be saved;",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 308.627,
      "end": 311.971,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Lord God will fulfil his covenants",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 312.151,
      "end": 314.427,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he has made unto his children;",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 314.607,
      "end": 318.369,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and for this cause the prophet has written these things.",
      "verse": "6:12",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 319.049,
      "end": 328.755,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, they that fight against Zion",
      "verse": "6:13",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 328.935,
      "end": 331.489,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the covenant people of the Lord",
      "verse": "6:13",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 331.669,
      "end": 334.27,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall lick up the dust of their feet;",
      "verse": "6:13",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 334.45,
      "end": 338.119,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the people of the Lord shall not be ashamed.",
      "verse": "6:13",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 338.299,
      "end": 341.968,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the people of the Lord are they who wait for him;",
      "verse": "6:13",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 342.148,
      "end": 345.213,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they still wait for the coming of the Messiah.",
      "verse": "6:13",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 345.893,
      "end": 349.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, according to the words of the prophet,",
      "verse": "6:14",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 349.835,
      "end": 354.525,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Messiah will set himself again the second time to recover them;",
      "verse": "6:14",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 354.705,
      "end": 358.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, he will manifest himself unto them",
      "verse": "6:14",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 358.182,
      "end": 360.69,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in power and great glory,",
      "verse": "6:14",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 360.87,
      "end": 363.285,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the destruction of their enemies,",
      "verse": "6:14",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 363.465,
      "end": 367.041,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when that day cometh when they shall believe in him;",
      "verse": "6:14",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 367.221,
      "end": 370.518,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and none will he destroy that believe in him.",
      "verse": "6:14",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 371.198,
      "end": 374.96,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they that believe not in him shall be destroyed,",
      "verse": "6:15",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 375.14,
      "end": 379.32,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both by fire, and by tempest, and by earthquakes,",
      "verse": "6:15",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 379.5,
      "end": 384.144,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by bloodsheds, and by pestilence, and by famine.",
      "verse": "6:15",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 384.324,
      "end": 387.296,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they shall know that the Lord is God,",
      "verse": "6:15",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 387.476,
      "end": 389.426,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Holy One of Israel.",
      "verse": "6:15",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 390.106,
      "end": 393.543,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For shall the prey be taken from the mighty,",
      "verse": "6:16",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 393.723,
      "end": 396.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or the lawful captive delivered?",
      "verse": "6:16",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 396.271,
      "end": 401.426,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For shall the prey be taken from the mighty, or the lawful captive delivered?",
      "verse": "6:16",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 402.106,
      "end": 403.731,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But thus saith the Lord:",
      "verse": "6:17",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 403.911,
      "end": 407.487,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Even the captives of the mighty shall be taken away,",
      "verse": "6:17",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 407.667,
      "end": 411.057,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the prey of the terrible shall be delivered;",
      "verse": "6:17",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 411.237,
      "end": 414.488,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Mighty God shall deliver his covenant people.",
      "verse": "6:17",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 414.668,
      "end": 416.34,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For thus saith the Lord:",
      "verse": "6:17",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 416.52,
      "end": 423.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will contend with them that contendeth with thee\u2014",
      "verse": "6:17",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 423.527,
      "end": 444.982,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But thus saith the Lord: Even the captives of the mighty shall be taken away, and the prey of the terrible shall be delivered; for the Mighty God shall deliver his covenant people. For thus saith the Lord: I will contend with him them that contendeth with thee-- and I will save thy children.",
      "verse": "6:17",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 445.662,
      "end": 450.027,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will feed them that oppress thee, with their own flesh;",
      "verse": "6:18",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 450.207,
      "end": 454.99,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall be drunken with their own blood as with sweet wine;",
      "verse": "6:18",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 455.17,
      "end": 457.213,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all flesh shall know",
      "verse": "6:18",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 457.393,
      "end": 461.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I the Lord am thy Savior and thy Redeemer,",
      "verse": "6:18",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 461.845,
      "end": 463.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Mighty One of Jacob.",
      "verse": "6:18",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 463.929,
      "end": 481.669,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will feed them that oppress thee, with their own flesh; and they shall be drunken with their own blood as with sweet wine; and all flesh shall know that I the Lord am thy Saviour Savior and thy Redeemer, the Mighty One of Jacob.",
      "verse": "6:18",
      "lineIndex": 118
    }
  ]
